wn glycolipid.</s><s>The predominant menaquinone(s) are MK-8 and MK-9 or MK-8.</s><s>The major cellular fatty acids are anteiso-C<sub>15 : 0</sub> and iso-C<sub>15 : 0</sub> or anteiso-C<sub>15 : 0</sub>.</s><s>The DNA G+C content is 53–58 mol%.</s></p></content></protolog>